\'93Yes,\'94 said Ed Thatcher as they stepped out on the pavement, \'93it\'92s a\
great moment.\'94\
\
\'93Vill yous allow me sir to invite you to drink a congradulation drink\
mit me?\'94\
\
\'93Why with pleasure.\'94\
