\
\'93An he said, Margie I\'92ve got a crush on you so bad, an she said, Come\
in outa the rain, you\'92re all wet....\'94 Voices coming down the stairs, a\
man\'92s feet in button shoes, a girl\'92s feet in sandals, pink silk legs;\
