The voices trailed out down the stairs.\
\
Jimmy Herf gave the bell another jab.\
\
\'93Who is it?\'94 came a lisping female voice through a crack in the door.\
\
\'93I want to see Miss Prynne please.\'94\
\
Glimpse of a blue kimono held up to the chin of a fluffy face. \'93Oh I\
don\'92t know if she\'92s up yet.\'94\
\
\'93She said she would be.\'94\
\
\'93Look will you please wait a second to let me make my getaway,\'94 she\
