\
The bathroom door opened; a stream of sunlight reflected out of\
a pierglass cut the murky hall in half, out of it came a head of\
hair like copper wire, bluedark eyes in a brittle-white eggshaped\
face. Then the hair was brown down the hall above a slim back in a\
