\'93Hullo Ruth.\'94\
\
\'93You can come in if you promise not to look.... I\'92m a sight and my\
room\'92s a pigeon.... I\'92ve just got to do my hair. Then I\'92ll be ready.\'94\
The little gray room was stuffed with clothes and photographs of stage\
