\
\'93Well how\'92s the cub reporter?\'94\
\
\'93I\'92m on Hell\'92s Kitchen.... It\'92s swell. Got a job yet Ruth?\'94\
\
\'93Um-um.... A couple of things may materialize during the week. But they\
wont. Oh Jimmy I\'92m getting desperate.\'94 She shook her hair loose of\
