\
\'93I\'92m going to eat a small steak and onions.\'94\
\
\'93Not if you\'92re intending to spend the afternoon with me Mr. Herf.\'94\
\
\'93Oh all right. Ruth I lay my onions at your feet.\'94\
\
\'93That doesn\'92t mean I\'92m going to let you kiss me.\'94\
\
\'93What ... on the Palisades?\'94 Ruth\'92s giggle broke into a whoop of\
